      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but 1200mg in a day feels like nothing when i'm literally crying from the pain. i read online that doctors sometimes prescribe much higher doses for severe inflammation. if i really need to get through the night and i can't get to a doctor until tomorrow, isn't it better to just take a higher dose now to get it under control than to suffer like this? just tell me what the upper limit really is so i can actually sleep.",
